  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.8.7">
<l>koṇṭā ṉēḻviṭai</l>
<l>yuṇṭā ṉēḻvaiyan</l>
<l>taṇtā mañceyteṉ</l>
<l>ṉeṇṭāṉā ṉāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who took the seven bulls,</l>
<l>he who ate the seven worlds,</l>
<l>making it a cool place</l>
<l>he himself became my thoughts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
